articles.author: Marc Jones
articles.title: Shares and euro climb ahead of ECB rate meeting - Reuters
articles.description: World shares were at a 15-month high and the euro climbed on Thursday as focus shifted from a widely-expected nudge up in U.S. interest rates to what is almost certain to be a similar move by the European Central Bank later.
